OL,3,CSussex Wildlife Trust demands action
OL,4,Cafter bio-bead pollution hits 50 mile
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FThe meeting comes after the plastic
OL,8,Fpellets, which are used to clean
OL,9,Fwastewater - spilled into the sea when
OL,10,Ffilters failed at Southern Water's
OL,11,Fwastewater treatment works in
OL,12,FEastbourne almost a month ago.
OL,14,FThe tiny black beads have now been
OL,15,Ffound along a 50 mile stretch of
OL,16,Fcoastline - from Eastbourne, across
OL,17,Fthe beaches of Camber and along St
OL,18,FMary's Bay in Kent. Cleanup work is
OL,19,Fongoing at the site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
