OL,7,FAfter the meeting, Corrigan said he
OL,8,Fwas encouraged the water firm was
OL,9,Ftaking responsibility for the incident.
OL,11,FHe said: "In terms of the clean up,
OL,12,Fthey (Southern Water) were very clear
OL,13,Fthat they've taken full responsibility
OL,14,Ffor the incident and they will pay in
OL,15,Ffull for the costs of the clean up,
OL,16,Fand that was a clearly an important
OL,17,Fpoint from our conversation today.
OL,26,@tD@FpmtD@Upn
