OL,7,FHe continued: "Clearly it is an issue
OL,8,Fthat water companies should pay for,
OL,9,Fand there should be the mechanisms to
OL,10,Fmake sure that happens.
OL,12,F"It shouldn't fall on us poor bill
OL,13,Fpayers, particularly when there are
OL,14,Ffailures, as there have been in this
OL,15,Fcase.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
