OL,7,F"And similarly, the removal of
OL,8,Fbiobeads and changing technology,
OL,9,Fthere will be a cost with that, but
OL,10,Fclearly is a cost with not doing it,
OL,11,Fas we have seen with this latest
OL,12,Fincident."
OL,14,FSouthern Water has not yet provided an
OL,15,Fupdate since the meeting, but has
OL,16,Fpreviously said: "Biobeads were the
OL,17,Fbest available technology when sites
OL,18,Fsuch as Eastbourne were constructed in
OL,19,Fthe 1990s.
