OL,4,Cafter bio-bead pollution hits 50 mile
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,F"Our newer sites use membrane sheets
OL,8,Fto do the same job.
OL,10,FReplacing bio-beads at the five out of
OL,11,F367 Southern Water wastewater
OL,12,Ftreatment plants that use them is
OL,13,Fbeing considered as part of the
OL,14,Findependent review we have
OL,15,Fcommissioned into the Eastbourne
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,F"To switch bead sites to membranes
OL,19,Fwould require major additional
OL,20,Finvestment and regulatory approval.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
