OL,7,F"An alternative would be to replace
OL,8,Fthe plastic beads with different
OL,9,Fmaterials."
OL,11,FIt's also understood that the results
OL,12,Fof an independent report considering
OL,13,Fthe future of bio-beads within
OL,14,FSouthern Water will be made available
OL,15,Fto the public once completed.
